title: Dead or Alive: Xtreme Beach Volleyball Comic Anthology
original_name: DEAD OR ALIVE XTREME BEACH VOLLEYBALL コミックアンソロジー
sinopse:
A Dead or Alive Xtreme manga was released in Japan. This black and white manga takes place in the Dead or Alive universe, covering the beach volleyball tournament. All of the girls are present in a large variety of cute swimsuits from the game.

(Source: deadoralive.wikia)
